SMITE: Single Molecule Imaging Toolbox Extraordinaire (MATLAB)

https://github.com/LidkeLab/smite

v0.2.0

Main subject: Fluorescent microscopy single-molecule imaging

A shortened version of this paper has been accepted by the Biophysical Society
2023 Annual Meeting for a non-peer reviewed poster presentation.

The software is used to analyze nanometer resolution single-molecule microscopy
data taken from static biological structures and dynamic interactions.
